                  </hi>. I am a super numerary City policeman. On the 22nd of Jan. I saw the prisoner on Tower-hill—I saw him, with another, go up to the prosecutor's pocket, take a handkerchief out of his right-hand pocket, and pass it into his own breeches-pocket—I took him by the col<lb></lb>lar, and, before he could get it into his pocket, took it from him—it, was in his pocket and in his hand also.</p>
